The meta-package piernik-mpich2-0-fedora.noarch.rpm contains dependencies on
everything that is necessary for compiling Piernik setups on a Fedora 15 and
later.  To install an environment for using the Piernik code on a Fedora,
use the following command (or equivalent):

sudo yum localinstall piernik-mpich2-0-fedora.noarch.rpm 
 
